		<legis-type>A BILL</legis-type>
		<official-title>To transfer recreational management authority for Lake Berryessa in the State of California from
			 the Bureau of Reclamation to the Bureau of Land Management, and for other
			 purposes.</official-title>
	</form>
	<legis-body id="H90EF442ED5E14B578D931C6EEDA4F9A5" style="OLC">
