        <header>Short title</header>
        <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">This Act may be cited as the <quote>
            <short-title>
              <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Lake Berryessa Recreation Enhancement Act of 2014" proposed="true">Lake Berryessa Recreation Enhancement Act of 2014</cato:entity-ref>
            </short-title>
          </quote>.</text>
			</subsection>
      <subsection id="H2EF97CE52D394E2DBEE43B3F590EBA2B">
        <enum>(b)</enum>
        <header>Table of contents</header>
        <text>The table of contents for this Act is as follows:</text>
				<toc container-level="legis-body-container" lowest-bolded-level="division-lowest-bolded" lowest-level="section" quoted-block="no-quoted-block" regeneration="yes-regeneration">
